{"tid":2174742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"襲美領館經理 兇徒被捕","createTime":"2020-08-26T05:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T05:59:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4b66c842e8861784285e6128a669d967a2ffb65e","tid":2174742,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:36:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/7JQSQM7U7NFEBOKHCHZ2VUULF4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2F7JQSQM7U7NFEBOKHCHZ2VUULF4%2F&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=d03b9e27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2F7JQSQM7U7NFEBOKHCHZ2VUULF4%2F&h=5a78cee0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/7JQSQM7U7NFEBOKHCHZ2VUULF4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n襲美領館經理 兇徒被捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hOaZfn_E3FCTLkiJypiVDsS94ns=/1409x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7CZXRPKGKBDK7NZTMCXE35TNUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhOaZfn_E3FCTLkiJypiVDsS94ns%3D%2F1409x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7CZXRPKGKBDK7NZTMCXE35TNUE.jpg&h=7b0ed6d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美國駐港澳總領事館一名職員昨午遭一名本地漢揮拳襲擊受傷。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中美關係緊張之際，中環美國駐港澳總領事館一名美籍男經理，昨午沿花園道行落山期間，遭一名本地漢揮拳襲擊，事主頭破血流，負傷折返領事館呼救送院。警方聞訊趕抵兜截無果，五小時後，在屯門拘捕一名35歲涉案男子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傷者頭破血流<br />\n<br />\n美國總領事館發言人回覆本報查詢時，證實一名職員被不知名人士襲擊，職員。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，遇襲男子年約40多歲，美國籍，為美國領事館的設施經理。昨午。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n事主負傷返回領事館求救，職員大驚報警，大批警員趕抵在附近搜捕，但。。。。。。"},{"pid":"f14e20824ae996df31cb247ca7a977b7b2eb63dd","tid":2174742,"uid":286897,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:37:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fff4c0d188ca3073e35102019cfe192e215fecc9","tid":2174742,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:39:45.000Z","msg":"義和團都夠膽拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0b886393a2637b35899c5488e35cc2e0736e28","tid":2174742,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:41:23.000Z","msg":"又話加速？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次打鳩你<br />\n下次無咁輕手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下F35、海豹係咪紙老虎"},{"pid":"b31c7aacae44859537bae769fe2e9adb94c64e36","tid":2174742,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fff4c0d188ca3073e35102019cfe192e215fecc9","tid":2174742,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:39:45.000Z","msg":"義和團都夠膽拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:51:49.000Z","msg":"義和團歷史：<br />\n雖然慈禧係支持過義和團殺洋人<br />\n但洋人打入北京後，慈禧為求和，即刻同啲主戰派義和團大臣割𥱊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉曬啲主戰大臣去殺頭/充軍新疆，先平息洋人怒火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc6c810648eb1e167ad848b20b1f747b896fbbe","tid":2174742,"uid":276548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:59:05.000Z","msg":"三毛藍絲你D手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}